{"snp1.12:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 1.12 ","snp1.12:0.2":"Munisutta ","snp1.12:1.1":"Santhavato bhayam jatam, ","snp1.12:1.2":"niketa jayate rajo; ","snp1.12:1.3":"Aniketamasanthavam, ","snp1.12:1.4":"etam ve munidassanam. ","snp1.12:2.1":"Yo jatamucchijja na ropayeyya, ","snp1.12:2.2":"Jayantamassa nanuppavecche; ","snp1.12:2.3":"Tamahu ekam muninam carantam, ","snp1.12:2.4":"Addakkhi so santipadam mahesi. ","snp1.12:3.1":"Sankhaya vatthuni pamaya bijam, ","snp1.12:3.2":"Sinehamassa nanuppavecche; ","snp1.12:3.3":"Sa ve muni jatikhayantadassi, ","snp1.12:3.4":"Takkam pahaya na upeti sankham. ","snp1.12:4.1":"Annaya sabbani nivesanani, ","snp1.12:4.2":"Anikamayam annatarampi tesam; ","snp1.12:4.3":"Sa ve muni vitagedho agiddho, ","snp1.12:4.4":"Nayuhati paragato hi hoti. ","snp1.12:5.1":"Sabbabhibhum sabbavidum sumedham, ","snp1.12:5.2":"Sabbesu dhammesu anupalittam; ","snp1.12:5.3":"Sabbanjaham tanhakkhaye vimuttam, ","snp1.12:5.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:6.1":"Pannabalam silavatupapannam, ","snp1.12:6.2":"Samahitam jhanaratam satimam; ","snp1.12:6.3":"Sanga pamuttam akhilam anasavam, ","snp1.12:6.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:7.1":"Ekam carantam munimappamattam, ","snp1.12:7.2":"Nindapasamsasu avedhamanam; ","snp1.12:7.3":"Sihamva saddesu asantasantam, ","snp1.12:7.4":"Vatamva jalamhi asajjamanam; ","snp1.12:7.5":"Padmamva toyena alippamanam, ","snp1.12:7.6":"Netaramannesamanannaneyyam; ","snp1.12:7.7":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:8.1":"Yo ogahane thambhorivabhijayati, ","snp1.12:8.2":"Yasmim pare vacapariyantam vadanti; ","snp1.12:8.3":"Tam vitaragam susamahitindriyam, ","snp1.12:8.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:9.1":"Yo ve thitatto tasaramva ujju, ","snp1.12:9.2":"Jigucchati kammehi papakehi; ","snp1.12:9.3":"Vimamsamano visamam samanca, ","snp1.12:9.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:10.1":"Yo sannatatto na karoti papam, ","snp1.12:10.2":"Daharo majjhimo ca muni yatatto; ","snp1.12:10.3":"Arosaneyyo na so roseti kanci, ","snp1.12:10.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:11.1":"Yadaggato majjhato sesato va, ","snp1.12:11.2":"Pindam labhetha paradattupajivi; ","snp1.12:11.3":"Nalam thutum nopi nipaccavadi, ","snp1.12:11.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:12.1":"Munim carantam viratam methunasma, ","snp1.12:12.2":"Yo yobbane nopanibajjhate kvaci; ","snp1.12:12.3":"Madappamada viratam vippamuttam, ","snp1.12:12.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:13.1":"Annaya lokam paramatthadassim, ","snp1.12:13.2":"Ogham samuddam atitariya tadim; ","snp1.12:13.3":"Tam chinnagantham asitam anasavam, ","snp1.12:13.4":"Tam vapi dhira muni vedayanti. ","snp1.12:14.1":"Asama ubho duraviharavuttino, ","snp1.12:14.2":"Gihi daraposi amamo ca subbato; ","snp1.12:14.3":"Parapanarodhaya gihi asannato, ","snp1.12:14.4":"Niccam muni rakkhati panine yato. ","snp1.12:15.1":"Sikhi yatha nilagivo vihangamo, ","snp1.12:15.2":"Hamsassa nopeti javam kudacanam; ","snp1.12:15.3":"Evam gihi nanukaroti bhikkhuno, ","snp1.12:15.4":"Munino vivittassa vanamhi jhayatoti. ","snp1.12:15.5":"Munisuttam dvadasamam. ","snp1.12:15.6":"Uragavaggo pathamo. ","snp1.12:16.0":"Tassuddanam ","snp1.12:16.1":"Urago dhaniyo ceva, ","snp1.12:16.2":"visananca tatha kasi; ","snp1.12:16.3":"Cundo parabhavo ceva, ","snp1.12:16.4":"vasalo mettabhavana. ","snp1.12:17.1":"Satagiro alavako, ","snp1.12:17.2":"Vijayo ca tatha muni; ","snp1.12:17.3":"Dvadasetani suttani, ","snp1.12:17.4":"Uragavaggoti vuccatiti. "}